'''查克·托德'''（{{lang-en|'''Chuck Todd'''}}，全名：查爾斯·大衛·托德，{{bd|1972年|4月8日}}），是一位美國[[記者|記者]]，亦是[[全國廣播公司|全國廣播公司]]（NBC）新聞訪談節目《[[與媒體見面|與媒體見面]]》第十二代主持人。當主持之前，他曾擔任駐白宮記者。

==生平==
查克生於[[美國|美國]][[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]]南部城市[[邁阿密|邁阿密]]，父親全名斯蒂芬·蘭多夫·托德（{{lang|en|Stephen Randolph Todd}}），母親洛伊絲·謝裡（{{lang|en|Lois Cheri}}）是[[猶太人|猶太人]]<ref name="#1"/>，查克自小被視作猶太人般撫養<ref>{{cite web |last=Bloom |first=Nate |url=http://www.interfaithfamily.com/arts_and_entertainment/popular_culture/Interfaith_Celebrities_Nate_Silver_Another_Bond_and_Happy_Endings.shtml |title=Interfaith Celebrities: Nate Silver, Another Bond, and Happy End |publisher=InterfaithFamily |date=2012-11-13 |accessdate=2013-08-17 |archive-date=2012-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121121022651/http://www.interfaithfamily.com/arts_and_entertainment/popular_culture/Interfaith_Celebrities_Nate_Silver_Another_Bond_and_Happy_Endings.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.haaretz.com/jewish-world/jewish-world-news/1.612266 Haaretz: "Former 'Meet the Press' host David Gregory writing book on his Jewish faith" by Anthony Weiss] {{Wayback|url=http://www.haaretz.com/jewish-world/jewish-world-news/1.612266 |date=20150924161717 }} August 24, 2014</ref>。他畢業於{{link-en|邁阿密基利安高中|iami Killian Senior High School}}（{{lang|en|Miami Killian Senior High School}}），1990至1994年間獲音樂獎學金，演奏[[法國號|法國號]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Lipman|first=Joanne|title=Is Music the Key to Success?|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/10/13/opinion/sunday/is-music-the-key-to-success.html|accessdate=14 October 2013|newspaper=New York Times|archive-date=2021-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320204421/https://www.nytimes.com/2013/10/13/opinion/sunday/is-music-the-key-to-success.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並於[[喬治華盛頓大學|喬治華盛頓大學]]升學，主修政治學，副修音樂，但他最後沒有畢業<ref>{{cite web|title=GWU Non-degree Alumni|url=http://alumni.gwu.edu/prominent-alumni-school-non-degree-students|accessdate=1 September 2014|archive-date=2016-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160517093355/https://alumni.gwu.edu/prominent-alumni-school-non-degree-students|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

